config BR2_PACKAGE_THINGINO_FLOODLIGHTD
	bool "thingino-floodlightd"
	help
	  Userspace daemon for the Wyze Floodlight v2 (T41) CH554 MCU.

	  The floodlight white LEDs, the 3-zone PIR motion array and the
	  siren are managed by an external CH554 MCU on /dev/ttyS2.
	  floodlightd speaks the stock serial protocol: it reports PIR
	  motion (per zone) to a hook script and drives the floodlight
	  brightness in response to motion.

	  Requires UART2 (ttyS2) enabled in the device tree.

	  See docs/wyze-floodlightv2-mcu-protocol.md for the protocol.
